('Flooring contractor project values profit margins', 'Flooring contractor project values vary by material: Carpet $3-$12/sq ft (labor $2-$5), Luxury vinyl $4-$15/sq ft (labor $3-$8), Hardwood $8-$25/sq ft (labor $5-$12), Ceramic tile $8-$30/sq ft (labor $5-$15), Natural stone $15-$50/sq ft (labor $8-$25). Markup: Materials 50-100%, labor $40-$80/hour. Annual income: Solo installer $40,000-$70,000, Small contractor (2-5) $150,000-$400,000, Medium contractor (5-15) $500,000-$2M revenue. High-margin specialties: Custom work, restoration, commercial.', 'specialty_business', 'NATIONAL', 'flooring,project_values,markup,luxury_vinyl,natural_stone,profit_margins', 'high', 'intermediate', 'qualifier_network_specialist,urgent_operator', 'specialty_trades_research_2025'),

